      <scopecontent id="aspace_a8213f333bf30a9dc2f3641d91d6e587">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection documents society and events during the Spanish Civil War. Formats include magazines and comic books, handbills, pamphlets, broadsides, manuscripts, and toys. Both Nationalist and Republican perspectives are represented in the materials. Materials date between 1936-2011, with the bulk between 1936-1943.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
