                  <scopecontent id="aspace_adf7266d8307972363aae2af92876470">
                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Two handbills with the same title but different content. Vallecas, Madrid: Partido Comunista. One urges communists, socialists, anarchists and other Republicans to united in the Popular Front. The other urges recipients to join the DECA (Republican Special Aircraft Defence)</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
