               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_525ac1caf68d4f06218df7631e1aeaa5">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Manuscript record of an aerial bombing by the 120th Squadron of the Italian Aviazione Legionaria, 1937 August 6-28. The names of each pilot are shown with where they conducted operations. It is signed by the commander of the Squadron Group and by the commander of the Squadron. The manuscript is in red ink, indicating that all flights occurred at night.</p>
               </scopecontent>
