               </did>
               <scopecontent id="aspace_c8fb3f436e1e2a71351a84e614d4ca8c">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Seven sheets of apparent food ration coupons issued in Spain during the Civil War. However, due to the fact that both sides of the conflict are represented and the incompatibility of the artistic quality with the notion of rationing, these appear to be fantasy pieces. Shown are both Republican (including the Abraham Lincoln Brigade) and Falangist images, as well as images of many towns and regions of Spain.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
